rComments: This Prof is very nice and makes the course material to be simple and easy.Though, I think the textbook needs to be revised since there is a lot of errors. Prof definitely needs to be explain things better, since there material is quite simple but explains it really difficult way. However, Overall Good Prof, Highly recommended.

Tough material but he does everything reasonably possible to make it easier to understand. Has a genuine interest in actually having a fruitful discussion of the topic rather than just having you produce assignments for grades.

A nice man with engaging lectures, but he doesn't realize how many of his students have no math background. He'd fare better with clearer instruction and more explanation of jargon and technical terms. Also, his original textbook does not have nearly enough examples.
